id: xilinx-server
unit: test plan
_name: Xilinx server tests
_description:
    Combined manual and automated Xilinx project-specific tests for Ubuntu Server images.
include:
nested_part:
    xilinx-server-manual
    xilinx-server-automated
certification_status_overrides:
    apply blocker to .*

